  "WeaponCanUseDes": {
    "Array": [
      "Unleashes lead like lightning, steady as thunder in the hands of the brave.",
      "Its shots echo like a pack of wolves chasing ghosts through steel corridors.",
      "Built for one purpose—shatter what stands in front of you, body or spirit.",
      "The faster it fires, the harder it pulls its wielder into the chaos.",
      "Delivers death with precision, no matter how far or fast the target.",
      "Its muzzle flash is a funeral torch in a forgotten war.",
      "Fused from broken rifles and old grudges. It never breaks formation.",
      "Looks like an angel, screams like a demon.",
      "Each burst cuts the air like a burning fuse counting down.",
      "Built around the remains of a failed prototype. Now it hunts the living.",
      "Its fire speaks the names of those already buried.",
      "Trained assassins worship its silence more than its accuracy.",
      "Wields like thunder wrapped in fog.",
      "A song composed in casing, powder, and pain.",
      "It fires mercy at 900 rounds per minute.",
      "Lightweight. Lethal. And never forgives being dropped.",
      "Fires best at dusk, when shadows start to bleed.",
      "Where it fires, the crows never leave.",
      "Named after the last stand of a vanished unit. Still waiting to fall.",
      "Leaves behind waves of lead and silence."
    ]
  },
